-- Digital Cinema Destinations to Open Imax Theater in Arizona
-- B y   M i c h a e l   W h i t e
-- 2013-06-05T16:14:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-05/digital-cinema-destinations-to-open-imax-theater-in-arizona.html
Digital Cinema Destinations Corp.,
operator of the Digiplex cinemas, will open an Imax Corp. screen
at its multiplex in Surprise, Arizona.  The theater will open on June 14, Westfield, New Jersey-based Digital Cinema said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michael White in Los Angeles at 
